StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [DeleteSMCRReserveUnitFromCollegePro.le]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@SMCRReserveUnitID uniqueiden..er, @CollegePro.leID uniqueiden..er
AS SET NOCOUNT ON
IF EXISTS (SELECT '1' from [MCRISS].[USMC].[CollegePro.leSMCRReserveUnit] where SMCRReserveUnitID = @SMCRReserveUnitID and @SMCRReserveUnitID IS NOT NULL and CollegePro.leID = @CollegePro.leID and @CollegePro.leID IS NOT NULL)
BEGIN
DELETE [MCRISS].[USMC].[CollegePro.leSMCRReserveUnit] WHERE SMCRReserveUnitID = @SMCRReserveUnitID AND CollegePro.leID = @CollegePro.leID END
--- CLEAN UP SET NOCOUNT OFF
